data.description: Presenting a remarkable investment opportunity in Athol, MA within minutes of Lake Ellis. This four-family residence offers an impressive return on investment with a remarkable potential cash flow. The units have been freshly painted and many details in each units have been updated. The roof, which was replaced in 2017, adds a layer of security and assurance. The bathroom on the second floor has been carefully renovated and the new flooring installed in many of the units adds a modern touch. The property also offers ample parking with space for 7-8 cars. Situated in a growing market, this property presents a unique combination of convenience and profitability for any aspiring investor. Benefit from a positive cash flow from this property and a near 10% CAP Rate.
